snippet.title: Whisker Squadron: Survivor (Demo Gameplay)
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay video of "Whisker Squadron: Survivor" demo version. An intense shooter with survival roguelike elements, from the creators of RACE THE SUN. You're a Whisker Squadron pilot, and your plan is simple: Wreak vengeance on The Swarm, and try to survive.

Developer: Flippfly LLC
Publisher: Flippfly LLC
Genre: Action, Adventure, Indie, On-Rails Shooter
Release Date: Q1 2023
Reviewed on: PC/Windows
Available on: PC/Windows

You can find Whisker Squadron: Survivor here: 
🕹️Steam► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2140100/Whisker_Squadron_Survivor/
